 methodology, , Copenhagen, Denmark: Danish EPA; Kirkeby, J.T., (2005) Modelling of life cycle assessment of solid waste management systems and technologies, , PhD dissertation, E&R Department, Technical university of Denmark DTU; Christensen, T.H., Bhander, G.S., Lindvall, H., Larsen, A.W., Fruergaard, T., Damgaard, A., Manfredi, S., Hauschild, M.Z., (2007) Experience with the use of LCA-modelling (EASEWASTE.) in waste management, Waste Management and Research Journal, 25, pp. 257-262; Hansen, T.L., (2005) Quantification of environmental effects from anaerobic treatment of source-sorted organic household waste, , PhD dissertation, E&R Department, Technical University of Denmark DTU","Bhander, G. S.; Department of Manufacturing Engineering and Management, Technical University of Denmark, 2800 Kongens Lyngby, Denmark",,,,,,,,02784491,,ENVPD,,"English","Environ. Prog.",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-52749094984
